snippet.title: Amber Heard arrested for domestic violence in 2009 - Hollywood TV
snippet.description:
Click to Subscribe! - http://bit.ly/SubHTV 
Hollywood TV is your source for daily celebrity news and gossip!
Amber Heard was reportedly arrested for domestic violence in 2009 after a fight with her girlfriend. Heard and Tasya van Ree got into an argument at the Seattle-Tacoma International airport and Heard allegedly hit her then girlfriend in the arm. According to TMZ she was charged with misdemeanor domestic violence but the prosecutor declined to move forward with the case because the couple were residents of California. 

Amber Rose and Wiz Khalifa have reached a settlement in their divorce. According to court documents Amber will get a cool million as outlined in the prenup she signed. The rapper will also pay her $14,800 a month in child support for their 3-year-old son Sebastian. The couple share legal and physical custody of their son. 

The Playboy mansion has been sold. Hugh Hefner's neighbor bought the legendary home. The mansion was purchased by Playboy Enterprises in 1971 for just over a million dollars. The sale comes with the condition that Hefner will be able to remain in the home as long as he lives. The home was listed for $200 million but no purchase price has been released.
